title: [To rel/0.13][IOTDB-2864] Fix Read-only occurred when insert Text values to aligned timeseries
[IOTDB-2864] Fix Read-only occurred when insert Text values to aligned timeseries
body:
## Description

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/25913899/162470614-b4048ae8-cb85-45d8-8ca7-7d8cf9f9e6b6.png)

When extending column in AlignedTVList, we need to supply bitmaps for the extending column. There is a bug causes the last supplying bitmap doesn't be marked, which will cause NPE when the extending column is TEXT dataType and execute flushing. Finally the server will turn to read-only because of it.

title: [IOTDB-2817] Clear Compaction Framework
body:
See [IOTDB-2817](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/IOTDB-2817).
Though the compaction framework is refactored in 0.13, there is still some poorly structured code. This PR does the following work:
- Clean the compaction package structure. For example, move all the classes which end with "Manager" to the root package of compaction.
- Abstract the compaction execution process. Abstract the static method `Compact` in the `CompactionUtils` into the `CompactionPerformer` class.
-  Abstract the `CompactionTaskComparator`  to facilitate multiple compaction task priorities.
- Seperate `InnerSpaceCompactionSelector` into `InnerSequenceSpaceCompactionSelector` and `InnerUnsequenceSpaceCompactionSelector`
- Remove `SizeTieredCompactionTask` and `RewriteCrossSpaceCompactionTask`.

ScalaTest 3.0.9 is a point release of ScalaTest that backported critical bug fixes and a few enhancements from 3.1.x.

Changes included:

  • Only expect non-filtered Async tests to be reported as completed in AsyncEngine, ParallelTestExecution and RandomTestOrder, which causes incorrect test count reported.

title: [To new_sync][IOTDB-2830] SQL: SHOW PIPE and SHOW PIPESERVER STATUS
body:
- 显示所有同步任务状态
  - create time，pipe的创建时间
  - name，pipe的名字
  - role，当前IoTDB在pipe中的角色，可能有两种角色：
    - sender，当前IoTDB为同步发送端
    - receiver，当前IoTDB为同步接收端
  - remote，pipe的对端信息
    - 当role为receiver时，这一字段值为发送端ip
    - 当role为sender时，这一字段值为pipeSink名称
  - status，pipe状态
  - message，pipe运行信息，当pipe正常运行时，这一字段通常为空，当出现异常时，可能出现两种状态：
    - WARN状态，这表明发生了数据丢失或者其他错误，但是Pipe会保持运行
    - ERROR状态，这表明发生了网络长时间中断或者接收端出现问题，Pipe被停止，置为STOP状态

title: [IOTDB-2818] Fix exception occurs when submitting compaction task to global queue
body:
The detail see [IOTDB-2818](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/IOTDB-2818)

The reason for this bug is as follow. When submitting a compaction task to global queue, system doesn't check the status of TsFileResource and just set it to `COMPACTION_CANDIDATE`. It will not check if the tsfile is closed until the task is submitted to be executed. In [PR-5198](https://github.com/apache/iotdb/pull/5198), we combine multiple status flags for TsFileResource into one enum variable, and check the status transition of the TsFileResource. If a TsFileResource status is `UNCLOSED`, it cannot be set to `COMPACTION_CANDIDATE`. So we need to check if the TsFileResource is `UNCLOSED` before we set it to `COMPACTION_CANDIDATE`.

title: [IOTDB-2811] Fix compaction exception handle failure cause by deletion of storage group
body:
The detail report see [IOTDB-2811](https://issues.apache.org/jira/projects/IOTDB/issues/IOTDB-2811?filter=allopenissues)

If user deletes the storage group when it is executing compaction, the `CompactionExceptionHandler` may fail to handle exception because it find that both source files and target files are lost. Consequently, the system will be set to **read-only** because the `CompactionExceptionHandler` takes it as a very serious situation.
The solution is to collect the `Future` object when the compaction task is submitted to thread pool, and cancel the executing of compaction task before deleting a storage group.

title: [IOTDB-2810] Design and implementation of TsBlock and its builder

This pr mainly does six things:
1. move `TsBlock` related class from `server` module to `tsfile` module to avoid circular dependency.

4. add `ColumnBuilder` interface to build the coresponding `Column`
5. add `TsBlockBuilder` to build the whole `TsBlock`
